come of 10 million yen, and applicants must also have private health insurance.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 100.0}}, {"text": "The minimum annual income required for Japan's digital nomad visa is 10 million yen.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"A digital nomad lifestyle requires skills such as self-discipline, time management, and investing skills, as well as the ability to manage one's own schedule in non-traditional work settings.\"", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "A digital nomad lifestyle requires skills such as self-discipline and time management to balance work and life while working remotely.", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"A digital nomad lifestyle requires skills such as self-discipline, time management, planning, and decision-making, as well as the ability to remain calm and solve problems when faced with challenges like internet connectivity issues.\"", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"A digital nomad lifestyle requires self-discipline, time management, and strategic integration of work and life, as individuals work in non-traditional settings and manage their own schedules.\"", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "To become a digital nomad, one needs to have the financial means to support their lifestyle, which can be achieved through investing and creating passive income, in addition to self-discipline and time management.", "citations": {"60aa4cb5-342f-4247-8498-89094bcd2d2d_720028489": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Digital nomads can stay in Japan for up to six months under the new visa program, which aims to promote domestic consumption and attract high-level technicians and technology engineers who work remotely.\"", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_84