nefit from their lifestyle by gaining high income, freedom, and broader perspectives and life experiences through remote work and travel.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 80.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads benefit from their lifestyle by earning a high income and having the freedom to work remotely, which allows them to gain broader perspectives and life experiences.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 80.0}}, {"text": "36% of Americans still believe in the American dream, which is the idea that if you work hard, you will get ahead.", "citations": {"bca53d85-08d2-4dec-b69b-658adc384e09_441583390": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"A recent poll found that 36% of Americans still believe in the American dream, which is the idea that hard work will lead to success.\"", "citations": {"bca53d85-08d2-4dec-b69b-658adc384e09_441583390": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"A recent poll found that 36% of Americans still believe in the American dream, which is defined as 'getting ahead with just a little effort'.\"", "citations": {"620614e1-45b7-4dad-8755-8e83ed16c830_220002243": 100.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads primarily work remotely, allowing them to travel and work from anywhere in the world without being tied to an office or strict schedule.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 100.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads primarily work remotely, using the internet to stay employed while traveling freely.", "citations": {"ce81a3b1-962d-402d-b926-4b9cbe19a4b2_209082205": 100.0}}, {"text": "The primary work arrangement of digital nomads is remote work, which allows them to work from anywhere and at any time, as long as they have an internet connection.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 100.0}}, {"text": "The primary work arrangement of digital nomads is remote work, which allows them to travel and live a location-independent lifestyle.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_375