i suggests that Indian herbal medicine, specifically Yoga and Ayurveda, may be effective in treating high-risk COVID-19 cases.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 80.0}}, {"text": "HealthRoots aims to treat various illnesses, including migraines, rheumatoid arthritis, and diabetes, using Ayurvedic remedies.", "citations": {"9070a5c5-cd76-46ba-8c07-33e91b535e03_742183461": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"HealthRoots uses Ayurvedic remedies to treat migraines, rheumatoid arthritis, and diabetes, showcasing the application of traditional Indian medicine in modern times.\"", "citations": {"9070a5c5-cd76-46ba-8c07-33e91b535e03_742183461": 80.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda has been researched for its potential in treating various health conditions, including mental health disorders.", "citations": {"e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793": 80.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda has been researched for treating mental health disorders, showing its relevance in modern medicine.", "citations": {"e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Ayurveda has been researched for its potential in treating mental health disorders, specifically anxiety in high-risk COVID-19 patients, and may aid in speedy post-treatment recovery.\"", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 80.0}}, {"text": "Traditional Indian medicine, including Yoga, has been found to have benefits in relation to mental health, particularly in reducing anxiety and improving overall well-being.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 60.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda, a form of traditional Indian medicine, has been studied for its potential in treating various conditions, including allergic rhinitis.", "citations": {"e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793": 80.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda has been studied for its potential in treating allergic rhinitis, indicating its possible application in modern Western medicine.", "citations": {"e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Rafah Herbal Medicine Center, directed by Dr. Nasser Hassanein, is providing herbal medicine treatment and seeing an increase in demand for alternative medicine in the Gaza Strip.", "citations": {"59dc9720-ded9-454e-a56f-7a838f8dd257_141302252": 80.0}}, {"text": "Dr. Nasser Hassanein's center is providing herbal medicine treatment.", "citations": {"59dc9720-ded9-454e-a56f-7a838f8dd257_141302252": 80.0}}, {"text": "The All India Institute of Ayurveda is collaborating with the London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine to study the effectiveness of Ashwagandha in treating long Covid.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 80.0}}, {"text": "The All India Institute of Ayurveda is likely involved in the study on Ashwagandha, given its prominence in the field of traditional Indian medicine.", "citations": {"893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Amrita Centre for Advanced Research in Ayurveda is an institution in India that researches Ayurveda.", "citations": {"aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846": 100.0}}, {"text": "The Amrita Centre for Advanced Research in Ayurveda is an institution in India that researches Ayurveda, with a focus on understanding how it can be deployed to better human health.", "citations": {"aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846": 100.0}}, {"text": "The Sreedhareeyam Ayurvedic Eyecare Hospital in India provides Ayurvedic eye treatment and has successfully helped a patient regain eyesight.", "citations": {"c61cb0fa-66d3-4423-a686-9dd2ff0a96a3_563900811": 100.0}}, {"text": "The Sreedhareeyam Ayurvedic Eyecare Hospital in Kerala, India, is an institution that provides Ayurvedic eye treatment, as evidenced by its successful treatment of Raila Odinga's daughter.", "citations": {"c61cb0fa-66d3-4423-a686-9dd2ff0a96a3_563900811": 90.0}}, {"text": "Shreedhareeyam Ayurvedic Eye Hospital in Kerala provides Ayurvedic eye treatment and has successfully treated patients, including Rosemary Odinga, who regained her vision after undergoing treatment.", "citations": {"f0653ab9-3cf9-417b-bc0a-b573a39c6c29_651867917": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Central Research Institute of Yoga & Naturopathy is being developed with an investment of Rs 100 crore, aiming to combine traditional knowledge of Yoga and Naturopathy with modern technology.", "citations": {"42883104-0bc6-428c-961b-f8057ba3a9ef_84142596": 100.0}}, {"text": "Rashtriya Ayurveda Vidyapeeth is an institution in New Delhi, India that promotes Ayurveda.", "citations": {"893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333": 100.0}}, {"text": "The Rashtriya Ayurveda Vidyapeeth (RAV) is an institution that promotes Ayurveda in New Delhi, India.", "citations": {"893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333": 100.0}}, {"text": "Rashtriya Ayurveda Vidyapeeth is an institution in New Delhi, India that promotes Ayurveda and has been involved in various projects, including telemedicine and documenting clinical cases.", "citations": {"893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Ayurvedic treatment methods include a combination of diet, herbs, massage, meditation, yoga, and cleansing, which can be applied in the treatment of various illnesses and are relevant to the context of traditional Indian medicine.\"", "citations": {"9070a5c5-cd76-46ba-8c07-33e91b535e03_742183461": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"Ayurvedic treatment methods include a combination of diet, herbs, massage, meditation, yoga, and cleansing, which can be applied in the treatment of various illnesses.\"", "citations": {"e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"Ayurvedic treatment methods include diet, herbs, massage, meditation, yoga, and cleansing, with herbs like Ashwagandha being used to boost energy, reduce stress, and strengthen the immune system.\"", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Ayurvedic t