on feed is to produce healthier fish by improving their growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "Replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients like yogurt in salmon feed can lead to healthier fish, faster growth, and reduced disease outbreaks.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "Replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients in salmon feed can lead to healthier fish, reduced breeding risk, and lower costs.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer, which was developed by Royal DSM for use in dairy cows.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer, which has been shown to reduce enteric methane emissions in cows.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer, as mentioned in the source document.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 60.00000000000001}}, {"text": "Omega 3 is a beneficial nutrient for heart health in farmed salmon.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Omega 3, specifically EPA and DHA, is beneficial for heart health in farmed salmon.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Omega 3 is a beneficial nutrient for heart health found in farmed salmon.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Lactobacillus B4 is a probiotic used in fish feed to enhance growth and improve resistance to pathogens.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 90.0}}, {"text": "Lactobacillus B4 is a probiotic used in fish feed to enhance growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5e