lmon feed in France.", "citations": {"2ac2bdd5-4221-4b59-9e27-a948f9f97ce0_1069242710": 80.0}}, {"text": "The bacteria used for producing feed additives in the new technology is Bacillus subtilis, which can be easily grown on waste grain production.", "citations": {"bb4fd768-e7a4-414b-9c8b-25e59edc3aa7_414881958": 100.0}}, {"text": "The bacteria used for producing feed additives in the new technology is Bacillus subtilis, which is cultured in a nutrient medium with specific salts and bran.", "citations": {"bb4fd768-e7a4-414b-9c8b-25e59edc3aa7_414881958": 100.0}}, {"text": "Bacillus subtilis is the bacteria used for producing feed additives in the new technology.", "citations": {"bb4fd768-e7a4-414b-9c8b-25e59edc3aa7_414881958": 80.0}}, {"text": "The new salmon feed may include essential amino acids as a nutrient, which are produced by the bacteria of the species Bacillus subtilis.", "citations": {"bb4fd768-e7a4-414b-9c8b-25e59edc3aa7_414881958": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"The new salmon feed includes essential amino acids, such as methionine, which is crucial for the growth of livestock animals and has a strong regulatory effect on animal metabolism.\"", "citations": {"33253149-3071-4359-aa80-aa606ec11c77_458600762": 80.0}}, {"text": "The new salmon feed includes essential amino acids and has a high protein content.", "citations": {"23d7fe7e-4589-40b8-b911-e83020b3b80b_318736858": 80.0}}, {"text": "The new salmon feed likely includes essential amino acids, such as methionine, to support the growth and development of salmon.", "citations": {"33253149-3071-4359-aa80-aa606ec11c77_458600762": 60.0}}], "references": ["8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929", "33253149-3071-4359-aa80-aa606ec11c77_458600762", "19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801", "6228349a-be88-4a0a-b280-320759afcd75_1005456136", "bb4fd768-e7a4-414b-9c8b-25e59edc3aa7_414881958", "f5d0e854-eb55-4d44-ab24-b5048804780e_793015685", "88e1620b-05e4-4676-b96c-ba056e1a081f_297756784", "39b66508-c08e-4