": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin discussed the Ukraine crisis, with Modi suggesting direct talks between Putin and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy to promote peace efforts.", "citations": {"11a1b39a-a673-4027-a029-17eb0e516745_73882007": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin discussed regional and global issues, including the Ukraine crisis, BRICS, and the global food market, and expressed interest in intensifying bilateral ties.", "citations": {"6df10203-b6bf-4015-8026-0171eb5efaca_46538679": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin last met in person in 2022 at the Shanghai Cooperation Organisation (SCO) Summit in Samarkand, Uzbekistan.", "citations": {"38219dc2-d65e-41cb-aa65-16a9b8d1a2a2_280122184": 100.0}}, {"text": "India and Russia aim to achieve a bilateral trade volume of 30 billion U.S. dollars by 2025.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 100.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 100.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"ea97d66c-aef3-451a-98a6-59f0c7b366c3_225244470": 100.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is 30 billion US dollars, as stated in a joint statement issued after a meeting between the two countries.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_919335038": 100.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_919335038": 100.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin discussed regional and global security, including military cooperation and defense agreements, during their meeting, which was focused on strengthening the India-Russia relationship.\"", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin are expected to discuss regional and global security, including joint military exercises, as well as the COVID-19 pandemic and Omicron variant during their meeting.\"", "citations": {"ea97d66c-aef3-451a-98a6-59f0c7b366c3_225244470": 80.0}}, {"text": "Modi and Putin will discuss regional and global security issues during their meeting.", "citations": {"fee5418e-ebb4-4f1d-b894-15cad92e7012_701474672": 80.0}}, {"text": "The meeting between Modi and Putin is expected to cover various international issues, including regional and global security, and will result in a joint political statement that highlights the importance of bilateral relations between India and Russia.", "citations": {"2c5e220c-554d-45c3-85a2-b6abc7897109_660385526": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin's meeting will likely focus on regional and global security, COVID-19 pandemic, and bilateral ties, building on their past discussions and cooperation.\"", "citations": {"6df10203-b6bf-4015-8026-0171eb5efaca_46538679": 80.0}}, {"text": "India has agreed to procure the S-400 missile system from Russia, among other equipment, to counter China.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "India is procuring military equipment from Russia, including nuclear-powered submarines, S-400, and AK-203, highlighting the ongoing importance of the India-Russia relationship in defense cooperation.", "citations": {"76ea5cd5-b2de-4145-a40b-be0ab18fa95c_99407596": 80.0}}, {"text": "The total trade value between India and Russia last year was over $50 billion or 65 billion dollars, indicating an expansion in trade between the two countries.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "The total trade value between India and Russia last year was over $50 billion.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Prime Minister Narendra Modi is scheduled to visit Moscow on July 2, 2024, to meet with Vladimir Putin, aiming to reaffirm bilateral relations and counter China's growing influence in the region.\"", "citations": {"8fa58a36-330a-43f1-b8b1-1b3ec51f7ad8_406552592": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Narendra Modi is scheduled to visit Moscow next week for bilateral talks with Russian President Vladimir Putin.", "citations": {"1240a670-880b-43a4-88bc-5e5f103bd6a1_229814010": 80.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin held talks in Moscow.", "citations": {"41c667f2-b1a7-4511-85c7-93f59700bd86_63948753": 100.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin will hold talks in New Delhi, India, where they are expected to sign a defense agreement and discuss cooperation in energy, space, and the Arctic.", "citations": {"71ec649d-a461-4230-ab97-ccd7f3699037_266520188": 90.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin will hold talks in Moscow.", "citations": {"6eb10358-9980-414c-91fb-8abc81461c5a_661214649": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin held talks in New Delhi, India, where they discussed bilateral relations and issued a joint statement calling for closer cooperation in support of JCPOA talks in Vienna.\"", "citations": {"09a3fee9-d8bc-4d37-bf6d-144412972cea_111458900": 90.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin will likely hold talks in India, as Putin is visiting the country and meeting with Modi to discuss various cooperation agreements.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation in various areas, including political, strategic, economic, and security cooperation, reaffirming their commitment to the Special and Outstanding Strategic Partnership.\"", "citations": {"b955247a-98fd-4d7a-bc42-c0683adb7b44_448016859": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have both emphasized the importance of expanding India-Russia cooperation, with Modi actively advocating for increased contacts and Putin recognizing Modi's contributions to strengthening the relationship between the two countries.\"", "citations": {"deba499a-e703-48ed-9cfa-527c88177b1c_305764772": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation, signing agreements on military and energy cooperation, and pledging to strengthen their bilateral relationship.\"", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation, with Putin considering India a friendly country and security ally.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "The leaders who have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation are Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin, as they have met to discuss defense and trade relations.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 80.0}}, {"text": "The current Russian Ambassador to India is Nikolai Kudashev.", "citations": {"2c5e220c-554d-45c3-85a2-b6abc7897109_660385526": 100.0}}, {"text": "The Russian Ambassador to India is Nikolai Kudashev.", "citations": {"2c5e220c-554d-45c3-85a2-b6abc7897109_660385526": 80.0}}, {"text": "The current Russian Ambassador to India is Denis Alipov, who has stated that the special Russia-India strategic partnership is growing stronger despite efforts to disrupt it.", "citations": {"ed16f6ac-89fe-4171-9739-9aeddba73e61_98192789": 80.0}}, {"text": "Nikolai Kudashev is the Russian Ambassador to India, and he has been involved in discussions about the upcoming meeting between Putin and Modi.", "citations": {"ced1a452-a3c3-401b-8321-d36d7d1e572c_567947551": 80.0}}, {"text": "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has been invited to visit Russia in 2024 by President Putin.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has been invited to visit Russia next year, as stated by Russian President Vladimir Putin during a meeting with the Indian foreign minister.", "citations": {"7a3755f5-4e98-4b63-95d0-2e22553b2e67_588916771": 80.0}}, {"text": "Modi and Putin emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs.", "citations": {"09a3fee9-d8bc-4d37-bf6d-144412972cea_111458900": 100.0}}], "references": ["3b36a839-e0d6-4053-a192-63fbdf82e536_367812021", "ea97d66c-aef3-451a-98a6-59f0c7b366c3_225244470", "4422e4b5-56a0-4873-b526-4cbc634b153a_680922469", "d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_919335038", "41c667f2-b1a7-4511-85c7-93f59700bd86_63948753", "38219dc2-d65e-41cb-aa65-16a9b8d1a2a2_280122184", "fee5418e-ebb4-4f1d-b894-15cad92e7012_701474672", "1240a670-880b-43a4-88bc-5e5f103bd6a1_229814010", "6b3f245f-38c0-4127-b6a5-5cde15a39776_299997556", "2c5e220c-554d-45c3-85a2-b6abc7897109_660385526", "09a3fee9-d8bc-4d37-bf6d-144412972cea_111458900", "ced1a452-a3c3-401b-8321-d36d7d1e572c_567947551", "b1d95583-d08d-48ef-8d81-7a93455a0d3c_1011209226", "6eb10358-9980-414c-91fb-8abc81461c5a_661214649", "9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430", "4ff724c6-0122-4a1b-adf0-e28d967863c7_882892101", "7a3755f5-4e98-4b63-95d0-2e22553b2e67_588916771", "6df10203-b6bf-4015-8026-0171eb5efaca_46538679", "614b97d3-73a1-4056-8643-bb4a28b93b74_940412328", "71ec649d-a461-4230-ab97-ccd7f3699037_266520188", "ed16f6ac-89fe-4171-9739-9aeddba73e61_98192789", "8fa58a36-330a-43f1-b8b1-1b3ec51f7ad8_406552592", "b955247a-98fd-4d7a-bc42-c0683adb7b44_448016859", "deba499a-e703-48ed-9cfa-527c88177b1c_305764772", "997d5424-bf51-4cc8-b41c-9375c62d6653_332691072", "d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719", "76ea5cd5-b2de-4145-a40b-be0ab18fa95c_99407596", "11a1b39a-a673-4027-a029-17eb0e516745_73882007"]}
